===Etymology===
{{prefix|en|hetero|normativity}}

===Noun===
{{en-noun|~}}

# The [[assumption]] that all human beings are either male or female in both [[sex]] and [[gender]], and that sexual and romantic attraction and activity only occurs, or is only normal, between people of different sexes.

